# Minimal valid .tq (tq_v1): intent → requires → result → flow: (order is fixed).
# Full rules: docs/TQ_SURFACE_MAPPING.md — one-page summary: docs/TQ_AUTHOR_CHEATSHEET.md
# Copy this file, edit names, then: torqa surface your_file.tq   or   torqa build your_file.tq

intent demo_idle
requires username, password
result OK

flow:
